PS11752778.name: Water Inlet Valve
PS11752778.install_instructions:
1. Turn off water and power.
2. Remove the old valve.
3. Install the new valve.
4. Reconnect hoses.

PS11740307.install_instructions:

2. Snap firmly into place.
3. No tools required.
